    "default_locale": "en-US",
    "description": {
        "en-US": "Restores the charset menu removed in Thunderbird 91 and fixes an issue in Thunderbird 78:\n\nThe charset menu isn't working for Japanese charsets already in TB 78\n(<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1677104\">https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1677104</a>)\nand furthermore the charset menu has been removed in TB 91\n(<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1704749\">https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1704749</a>)\nand the new repair option isn't working at all\n(<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1713786\">https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1713786</a>).\n\nThis add-on restores the \"classic\" charset menu, maybe one day Thunderbird will fix automatic detection."
    },
